Deploy Debian Stretch:
Build 1 & 2 used https://forum.pine64.org/showthread.php?tid=4931 but has a timer bug.
Build 3 will test https://github.com/ayufan-pine64/linux-build/releases

SSH to pine@10.0.0.199
PW: pine

Change NIC to DHCP:
sudo su
echo "auto eth0
iface eth0 inet dhcp" > /etc/network/interfaces

Replace sources.list with working copy :P
echo "deb http://deb.debian.org/debian stretch main contrib non-free" > /etc/apt/sources.list
rm /etc/apt/sources.list.d/security-updates.list

reboot

Reconnect to IP issued by DHCP server.

** run NEMS system prep as normal

Resize filesystem:
/root/nems/nems-admin/resize_rootfs.sh

reboot


Compile NEMS as normal.
